item.content:encoded:
Amaze is a kind of leisure puzzle game. Players need to control small balls to escape in different level mazes. The color of each small ball is different. Fill in the blank area of the level in the game, choose the fastest path to play within the specified time, have a good time in Amaze!!!
Slide on the screen to play

item.content:encoded:
Nonogram is a puzzle game to exercise your brain. At the top of each column and on the side of each row you will see one or more numbered ensembles that tell you the order of the black squares, so if you see 10 1, this tells you there will be ten black squares, then one or more white squares, then one black square.
Click to operate
